window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mayah Jones is not your average bodyguard; she is known as the guardian of the stars. This is not new to her. This is her life—where fame meets danger, and passion ignites like flashbulbs on a star-studded night. Are you ready to walk the red carpet with Maya? It's a new and different experience for her and her client each time.</p> <p>It just so happens that this client once was a love of hers, and yes, this is a no-no in the industry. That is having relationships with one client.</p> <p>Mayah Jones's journey from personal protection to becoming a sought-after guardian was fueled by her dedication, competence, and the trust she earned from the entertainment industry's elite. Mayah Jones was the guardian to the stars, celebrities, and other VIPs who got wind of her through prestige gossip and confidential whispers. </p> <p>Great and noted as she is, there was but one Mayah Jones celebrity protector, but she is in demand, and on the advice of her main client, Mr. Hollywood himself, Wyatt W. Burrows, to train a specialized all-female protection team that mirrors her.<br> <br> The elite wanted her by their side during red carpet events, international travels, and everyday life. Not only she is lovely in appearance, mayah was skilled in what she does as a guardian within the shadows. Her name became synonymous with excellence in personal protection.</p> <p>Whether navigating the paparazzi, securing private events, or ensuring privacy, Mayah handled it gracefully and precisely.</p>"; 
